Bren Foster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bren_Foster 0 Bren Foster is an Australian actor. Best known for his lead in The Last Ship on TNT he is also a martial artist who holds black belts in taekwondo, hapkido, and hwarangdo. He was born on 2 November 1978.
